力不討好，如果暫時停左佢，大家將精力畀返落去16號，幫民陣宣傳既話，會更加effective，我個人係咁諗<br />\n至於具體點做，點去幫，都係果句，大家各自努力，我淨係比個方向only<br />\n<br />\n完<br />\n歡迎比意見"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T14:39:19.000Z","msg":"唯唯果邊話自己策劃人身份暴左，叫大家停一停"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T15:08:37.000Z","msg":"聽講唯萎係公海admin"},{"pid":"060587293db727b7b743205d7c43335b8fc791f1","tid":1217710,"uid":24173,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T15:09:47.000Z","msg":"以為自己開post<br />\n都真係幾攰 考慮緊"},{"pid":"653cef40bc73014bcb62b2525e93474d9c00c30b","tid":1217710,"uid":184389,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T15:11:21.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"c40ce823f5e155f6f0903f50aa18c1769c54af68","tid":1217710,"uid":45910,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T15:16:13.000Z","msg":"唔出儲民心"},{"pid":"a9b0641b312f04a21eb6483739eacb7cd0ea573b","tid":1217710,"uid":187493,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T15:16:37.000Z","msg":"我個人見解係，聽日要休息一下先，睇情況再緊急出動。<br />\n然後就去行多啲街盡快係星期日前認識多啲路。最緊要調整心態唔好太嬲，一直只係諗今次件事要放鬆一下。<br />\n但千其唔好放棄曬沒咗團火，我自己今日先嬲到流曬鼻血又頭痛咗成日。<br />\n各位加油<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2c88d6b57e67188c79b9ec601fd296bbc5f367d1","tid":1217710,"uid":9681,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T15:18:23.000Z","msg":"至少睇到堵塞嘅效果同吸收經驗<br />\n冇乜傳媒報道，如果可以作爲談判籌碼仲好<br />\n<br />\n頭盔純粹討論"},{"pid":"a1de1aaa0f31b7905f4c97376ada1cba7da6d59c","tid":1217710,"uid":237068,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T15:22:30.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"98d2bbf2da5d229cbdf36d14237c6a70182610e3","tid":1217710,"uid":159417,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T15:25:22.000Z","msg":"同內外一個講民意戰ge po 不謀而合"},{"pid":"cef7a223394a2a0aaa67ef8d09bba096954df068","tid":1217710,"uid":233791,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T15:26:13.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"f6be78b10c7b17f4ecdf39f16fe8c7e398982343","tid":